    sentence
    begin
      translation fr "Suite à beaucoup d’insistance de sa part, " M:+pro " a fini par laisser " P " être dans la confidence."
      translation en "Following a lot of insisting from " P:+cli ", " M:+pro " finally let " P:+cli " know about it."
      translation eo "Pro insistego el " P:+pro:+acc ", " M:+pro " finfine lasis " P:+pro:+acc " scii prie."
